Reamaze,is,a,lightweight,brandable,customer,support,service,that,allows,users,to,respond,to,any,type,of,customer,message,from,their,email,account,Response,templates,help,shorten,response,times,and,built,in,collision,detection,prevents,duplicate,responses,Users,can,create,public,knowledge,bases,and,forums,where,customers,can,search,for,their,own,answers,and,offer,feedback,Built,in,reporting,keeps,users,apprised,of,response,times,and,conversation,volume